snippet.title: Dos Equis Amber Review | Beer is Tasty
snippet.description:
Beer is Tasty: Bryan and Chris kick off a mexican themes batch of episodes with Dos Equis Amber ale! 

We enjoy a retrospective look at American classics such as Shirley Temple the actress and the beverage, and of course a quick shootout to The Sound of Music.

Find out if Dos Equis Amber goes amazing with chips'n salsa, or if it's like being kicked in the face during a punch fight.
